text: Novokangyshevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Uchpilinsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 423 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Dyurtyuli. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Novokangyshevo
